    <briefdescription>
<para>STM32 GPIO specific flags. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The driver flags are encoded in the 8 upper bits of <ref refid="group__gpio__interface_1gad435719dccdc37c05852960a7218fbd2" kindref="member">gpio_dt_flags_t</ref> as follows:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Bit 8: Configure a GPIO pin to power on the system after Poweroff.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Bit 10..9: Configure the output speed of a GPIO pin. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
